headline: Disney Ultimate Toy Drive Launches Company-wide Effort to Deliver Toys – and Happiness – to Children and Families Across the Country
summary: BURBANK, Calif., November 07, 2024--Today, The Walt Disney Company (NYSE: DIS) announced the launch of its company-wide 2024 Disney Ultimate Toy Drive supporting the Marine Toys for Tots Program, which has helped deliver millions of toys to children in need during the holiday season. Good Morning America (GMA) reported exclusively on the new campaign, highlighting three unsung heroes at Toys for Tots: Sergeant Christos Toromanides, GypC Serna, and Staff Sergeant Xavier Montaie.
